Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:41.45,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.79,Danna ga Nani Main,rino,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:43.66,Danna ga Nani Main,nozomu,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.62,Danna ga Nani Main,tanak,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:45.46,Danna ga Nani Main,yama,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.50,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Meus parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:47.46,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.71,Danna ga Nani Main,mom,0,0,0,,Parabéns.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:50.71,Danna ga Nani Main,dad,0,0,0,,Parabéns...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.88,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Boatos se espalham muito rápido.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.34,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Não fui eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.22,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Você está nervoso?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.47,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.60,Danna ga Nani Main,rino,0,0,0,,O que tiver que ser, será. \N Vocês ficarão bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.47,Danna ga Nani Main,nozomu,0,0,0,,Sim, exatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:07.73,Danna ga Nani Main,tana,0,0,0,,Estou aqui, não se preocupe. \N Farei tudo o que puder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:08.48,Danna ga Nani Main,yama,0,0,0,,Isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.48,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Então, como você se sente?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.29,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Não sinto como se fosse real.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.98,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Não consigo para de pensar \N se um cara como eu merece isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:18.99,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Como se talvez fosse \N um sonho e tudo fosse desaparecer amanhã.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.49,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Nada de errado irá acontecer. Não irei deixar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.62,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Não aceitarei esse destino...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.66,Danna ga Nani Main,miki,0,0,0,,Irei destruí-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.20,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Que manifesto de ódio camarada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:27.21,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.63,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Irei lhe fazer uma pergunta que \N não poderia responder a um ano atrás.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.96,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Ei, por que o Pai sempre está em casa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.76,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Porque ele trabalha em casa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:36.84,Danna ga Nani Main,mayo,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.51,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Rock you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.51,Danna ga Nani Main,Nota,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Trad. Literal: “Te detonei!”{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.51,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fsp4\blur0.8\fs45\b0\fnKG Ten Thousand Reasons\bord2\xshad-2\yshad2\c&HF7F7F7&\3c&H010102&\4c&H1B1A1A&\fscx119\fscy100\pos(130.267,162.667)}Eu não comprrendo o que \N meu marido está dizendo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.51,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fsp4\blur0.8\fs45\b0\fnKG Ten Thousand Reasons\bord0\c&HF7F7F7&\3c&H0B0B0B&\4c&H1B1B1C&\fscx119\fscy100\pos(130.267,162.667)}Eu não comprrendo o que \N meu marido está dizendo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.26,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Estou certo de que o resultado será apenas um mal entendido novamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.43,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Rápido! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.93,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Seja paciente...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.39,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Ah, eu não estou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.77,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Bem, ficará por conta dos deuses, afinal de contas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:49.39,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,Vê?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.06,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Ah, que pen— Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:55.90,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:08.53,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,Na realidade, \N a vida cotidiana não acaba tão dramaticamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.83,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,Vai junto ao silêncio, às vezes supera os limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.59,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,com uma mistura de felicidade e preocupação...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.09,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,Licença maternidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.09,Danna ga Nani Main,haji,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sankyuu (産休)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.13,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,{\an3}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.13,Danna ga Nani Main,kaoru,0,0,0,,{\an1}Trad. Literal: “Obrigada”. {Really? '-'}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.76,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,{\an8}Em tempos tranquilos e em tempos ocupados,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:27.32,Danna ga Nani Main I,haji,0,0,0,,{\an8}viver de modo banal continua sendo andar para frente, \N para nunca voltar para trás.
